dc_title_s: Carte de la Guinee contenant les Isles du Cap Verd, le Senegal, la cote de Guinee proprement dite, les royaumes de Loango, Congo, Angola et Benguela.
dc_description_s: Inset: Cote d'Or par le Sr. D'Anville. Map 42 from Vol. 2 of Atlas Universel by P. Santini. 1 map: col.; 43 x 57 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
